Happy Birthday

The current year is 2020. And it's your friends birthday. You know her name and the year of her birth. You want to wish her and remind her of her current age.

Input Format
A single line with 2 space separated inputs - name year

Output Format
A single line - "Happy Birthday <name>! Your current age is <computed_age>"

Examples
Sample Input
Ria 1996
Expected Output
Happy Birthday Ria! Your current age is 24
Constraints
Assume that the input satisfies these constraints.

0 < length of name <= 100
1980 <= year of birth < 2020
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
import java.util.*;
import java.lang.*;
import java.io.*;

// Please make sure not to delete the WorkAtTech class
// You can create additional non-public classes as well
// But the main method should be in the WorkAtTech class
class WorkAtTech
{
	public static void main (String[] args) throws java.lang.Exception
	{
		// your code goes here
		Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);
		
		String name = input.next();
		int age = input.nextInt();
        
		if (1980<=age){
			if(age<2020){
				age= 2020-age;
			}
		}
		
		System.out.println("Happy Birthday "+ name + "! Your current age is "+ age );
	}
}
